replies.body:
Overal the tank class (wardens mostly) need a rework. They should be tanky in teamfights (5v5) but more squishy outside that. Basicly items that makes them more tanky the more people are arround. To ballance this out these tank stats should scale with their other defensive items. I give an example:

* **ITEM A:** {{item:1028}} + {{item:1029}}
* **ITEM B:** ITEM A + {{item:1057}} 
 * **Unique passive:** Gain 2% bonus mr & armor for every nearby enemy champion.
